of equilibrium situations the current\ninduced forces can destabilize the mechanical vibrations and cause limit-cycle\ndynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2011 21:32:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2012 09:45:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-11"}
