above transition discs might be\ninterpreted as active planet and planetesimal forming regions situated far (>\n50 AU) from the central stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2011 11:54:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2011 08:44:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
